			<description><![CDATA[<p>
eRetailing Associates, a leading ecommerce personalization on demand apparel marketer is looking for Full-Time Customer Service Representatives for our Hilliard OH office.<br />
Candidates must have work availability between 9am-9pm, Monday through Friday, as well as some weekends.</p>
<p>
Customer Service Representative Job Duties:<br />
&bull; Attracts potential customers by answering product and service questions; suggesting information about other products and services<br />
&bull; Maintains customer records by updating account information<br />
&bull; Resolves product or service problems by clarifying the customer&#39;s complaint; determining the cause of the problem; selecting and explaining the best solution to solve the problem; expediting correction or adjustment; following up to ensure resolution<br />
&bull; Recommends potential products or services to management by collecting customer information and analyzing customer needs<br />
&bull; Prepares product or service reports by collecting and analyzing customer information<br />
&bull; Contributes to team effort by accomplishing related results as needed<br />
&bull; Independently solve customer issues without manager involvement</p>
<p>
Skills Qualifications:<br />
&bull; At least one year of customer service experience<br />
&bull; Product Knowledge<br />
&bull; Quality Focus<br />
&bull; Problem Solving skills<br />
&bull; Market Knowledge<br />
&bull; Documentation skills<br />
&bull; Phone etiquette skills<br />
&bull; Resolving Conflict<br />
&bull; Analyzing Information<br />
&bull; Multi-tasking abilities<br />
&bull; Computer knowledge<br />
&bull; Able to type at least 50wpm<br />
&bull; Internet knowledge and search abilities<br />
&bull; Ability to calmly assist customers</p>
<p>
Additionally, Customer Service Representatives will be responsible for gaining a strong knowledge of our websites, the products we offer, and the processes used in producing a custom order.</p>
<p>
Still interested?...........</p>
<p>
If so, and you meet these qualifications, please respond with your resume and cover letter.<br />
